{"tid":2255547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙螺灣係咪真係想獨立？","createTime":"2020-10-23T15:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T00:20:16.000Z","uid":25178,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a875aed69ec10e271e5a9617176530de8a526927","tid":2255547,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"天行足跡<br />\n13 小時  &middot; <br />\n<br />\n沙螺灣 建國大業：進度報告<br />\n<br />\n探子回報，近幾日沙獨分子在村的東西出入處加裝了兩道關口，並裝上了大門，準備隨時「全面封關」。東閘的頂上設置了帶鈎剌的鐵絲網，屬國境級防禦工程，可防止中國香港人翻牆偷渡入境。西閘的路由於早前已被擴闊為國家級幹道，工程人員正趕工在幹道兩旁堆置大石，現場並堆放了大量鐵絲網，準備圍封路旁的空地。由於本週進度突飛猛進，相信工程有望於週末完成，發揮保家衛國、保鄉衛族的積極作用！<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/skywalkersfootprints/posts/3178961255547727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fskywalkersfootprints%2Fposts%2F3178961255547727&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vFu%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=ee1435ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/skywalkersfootprints/posts/3178961255547727</a><br />\n藍色線係公家路<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/122233758_3178956142214905_704643205360449860_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=CToZVTrumaIAX_clF0V&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=2ab4dc9eeb0e7ead513446ec84423568&amp;oe=5FB8A890\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F122233758_3178956142214905_704643205360449860_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DCToZVTrumaIAX_clF0V%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D2ab4dc9eeb0e7ead513446ec84423568%26oe%3D5FB8A890&h=f76a660f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「天行足跡」呢個page一路查緊沙螺灣嘅事<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/skywalkersfootprints/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fskywalkersfootprints%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vFu%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=7aab3cef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/skywalkersfootprints/</a>"},{"pid":"9584dc5a81